data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! In-Town Land For Sale. 2 Blocks to Downtown Downers Grove, 1 Block to Prince Pond, 4 Blocks to the Main Street BNSF Express Train Station, & 4 Blocks to ALL 3 Top Rated public schools; Pierce Downer Elementary, Herrick Middle, & Downers North High School! 50x125 lot size in the heart of one of the most sought after Downers Grove Neighborhoods and situated on a historic brick street amongst MANY new construction homes. Property is being sold AS-IS. Value is in the land. Property is NOT located in a flood plain, Lake Michigan Water on site, public city sewer, curbed road, and sidewalks on both sides of the street. Great opportunity to build a future new construction home. Listing Agent must Confirm all Appointments to walk the property. NO INTERIOR TOURS OF THE PROPERTY. Don't miss this opportunity-Downtown Downers Grove Living at it's Finest!
